<br>
with PoP shmaan's slow should go from 75% to 80% ...<br>
it is &quot;only&quot; 5% more ... but it will go from 1 hit every 4 to 1 hit every 5 ... that's a huge improve.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
if you increase slow from 30 to 35% you go from hiting 14 times every 20 (0.7) to 13 hits every 20 (0.65). The increase is:<br>
(14-13)/13*100= 7.7%<br>
<br>
now if you increase slow from 90 to 95% you go from hiting 2 times every 20 (0.1) to hiting 1 time every 20 (0.05). The increase is:<br>
(2-1)/1*100 = 100%<br>
<br>
the slow isn't a linear thing...that's why slow at 75% is huge...and with PoP might become even better<br>
