<br>
You need 2 mages.<br>
<br>
You need 2 different level pets (gvoc-voc)<br>
<br>
The lower version pet will hold agro over the higher level pet.  The owner of the higher lvl pet can go melee w/o being touched.  Did it all the time from 35-50, would always end the battle with full health, heck you can even conservatively nuke while melee'ing in there and not gain agro.<br>
